<plot>Estranged from her mother and failing to cope with her father's terminal illness, ten year-old Tanya indulges in an imagined fantasy world. She believes that by bargaining with a Guardian living in her bathroom mirror, she will be granted a wish to save her father's life. When the sacrifice becomes too high a price to pay, Tanya must have the courage to face reality and her demons - those both real and imagined.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?371575</url></doc>
